{{#> layout
  title='Translate Words and Learn Them as Flashcards'
  url='/'
}}
  <div class="container-sm text-center">
    <div class="mb-5 p-2 bg-light d-none" id="encourageToTry">
      Hey, you can see how the browser extension works by simply selecting any word on this website and clicking the icon.
      <br />
      The translation will be provided in <select id="translationLanguage"></select>
    </div>
    <h1 class="mb-5">Translate new words while surfing the web or watching YouTube. Learn the translated words on your mobile.</h1>
    <div class="mb-5">
      Master the language by using it. Vocably will support
      you by automatically creating high-quality flashcards based on the
      words you translated. You can review and learn your words in
      the mobile app when you have time.
    </div>
    <div class="mb-3 text-center chrome-cta d-none">
      <a class="d-inline-flex px-4 py-2 align-items-center text-start btn btn-primary rounded-pill"
         href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/vocably/baocigmmhhdemijfjnjdidbkfgpgogmb"
         target="_blank"
      >
        <img src="assets/chrome.svg" alt="Google Chrome Logo" height="32" class="pe-3" />
        <span class="text-center">Install Chrome Extension</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-3 text-center safari-cta d-none">
      <a  class="d-inline-flex px-4 py-2 align-items-center text-start btn btn-primary rounded-pill"
          href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6464076425"
          target="_blank"
      >
        <img src="assets/safari.svg" alt="Safari Logo" height="32" class="pe-3" />
        <span>Install Safari Extension</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-3">
      <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/vocably-pro-language-cards/id1641258757" target="_blank" class="d-inline-block mb-2"><img src="assets/download-on-app-store.svg" alt="Download on App Store" height="40" /></a>
      <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vocablypro" target="_blank" class="d-inline-block ms-2 mb-2"><img src="assets/get-it-on-google-play.svg" alt="Get it on Google Play" height="40" /></a>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-5">
      <span class="text-dark">Vocably is <strong>100% free</strong>.</span>
      <button
        class="btn btn-link px-0 text-decoration-none"
        type="button"
        data-bs-toggle="collapse"
        data-bs-target="#whyItIsFree"
        aria-controls="whyItIsFree"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-label="Toggle navigation"
      >Why? <i class="bi-chevron-down icon-collapsed"></i><i class="bi-chevron-up icon-expanded"></i></button>

      <div class="bg-light collapse" id="whyItIsFree">
        <div class="p-4">
          Vocably is a 100% free product. It costs me around 150 euros every month.
          I created this project to help myself to learn Dutch by engaging in the Dutch web.
          It is helping me so much that I see these 150 euros as my monthly payment for using a fantastic tool.
          Also, Vocably is my <a href="https://github.com/vocably/vocably-pro" target="_blank">hobby project</a>, which is a win-win. Of course, I’d be happy to make it profitable.
          And I don’t know yet how I will do it. But I will do my best to keep it free for current users.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How it works-->
  <div class="container-sm text-center mb-5">
    <div class="h2 mb-5">How it works</div>
    <div class="mb-5" style="position: relative; width: 100%; padding-bottom: 56.25%;height: 0;">
      <iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/UwNog9yKCeA?si=GBITVvtufhM3HLKD&rel=0" title="How I use Vocably" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-4 pb-4 border border-1 border-start-0 border-top-0 border-end-0">
      <div class="col-1 fs-1 text-dark">1</div>
      <div class="col-6 text-start">
        Highlight an unfamiliar word while browsing any website on your desktop device.
      </div>
      <div class="col-5">
        <img class="img-fluid w-100 mb-4 mb-md-1" src="assets/img/how-it-works-01.svg" alt="Created flashcard">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mb-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-4 pb-4 border border-1 border-start-0 border-top-0 border-end-0">
      <div class="col-1 fs-1 text-dark">2</div>
      <div class="col-6 text-start">
        Vocably will automatically convert the word to the normal form (i.e. infinitive for a verb or singular for a noun), get its definitions, translations, and create high quality flashcards.
      </div>
      <div class="col-5">
        <img class="img-fluid w-100 mb-4 mb-md-1" src="assets/img/how-it-works-02.svg" alt="Created flashcard">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
      <div class="col-1 fs-1 text-dark">3</div>
      <div class="col-6 text-start">
        The created flashcards are available to be studied with Spaced
        Repetition System (SRS) method across all your mobile and desktop
        devices.
      </div>
      <div class="col-5">
        <img class="img-fluid w-100 mb-4 mb-md-1" src="assets/img/how-it-works-03.svg" alt="Created flashcard">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-sm pt-5 mt-5">
    <div class="h2 mb-5 text-center">Supported Languages</div>

    <p>You can learn <a href="https://cloud.google.com/translate/docs/languages" target="_blank">any language</a> with Vocably.</p>

    <p>But it works exceptionally well with Arabic, Czech, English, German, Danish, Greek, Spanish, French, Hebrew, Hindi, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Dutch, Norwegian, Polish, Portuguese, Russian, Swedish, Thai, Turkish, Traditional Chinese, and Simplified Chinese.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container-sm pt-5">
    <div class="h2 mb-5 text-center">About Vocably</div>

    <img src="assets/about.webp" class="float-start me-4 rounded-2" alt="Photo of Dima Snisarenko" width="40%" />

    <p>
      Hello, I'm Dima Snisarenko, an <a href="https://sneas.io" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">independent developer</a> from Ukraine living in the Netherlands since 2014.
    </p>

    <p>
      I built Vocably to fit my own needs in language learning. I tried many different methods, but the most effective one was using a Spaced Repetition System (SRS).
    </p>

    <p>
      Vocably has enabled me to learn Dutch by engaging in the Dutch web. Now I can read and understand news articles. Recently, I decided to work on my listening, thus I made Vocably to work with YouTube videos.
    </p>

    <p>
      Vocably has helped me a great deal with my language learning, and I hope it will help you too.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="py-5 text-center">
    <div style="font-size: 1rem;">
      Follow Vocably on social platforms
    </div>
    <div class="display-5 mt-3">
      <a href="https://github.com/vocably" class="text-decoration-none text-secondary" target="_blank">
        <i class="bi bi-github"></i>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/vocably" class="text-decoration-none text-secondary mx-2" target="_blank">
        <i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i>
      </a>
      <a href="https://twitter.com/VocablyPro" class="text-decoration-none text-secondary" target="_blank">
        <i class="bi bi-twitter"></i>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/vocably.pro" class="text-decoration-none text-secondary" target="_blank">
        <i class="bi bi-instagram"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

{{/layout}}

